          "name": "text1",
          "value": "These puzzles use a grid of numbers with a target sum. Find groups of two, three, or four numbers that add up to the target. The members of a group must share sides. Use tokens, such as different types of food items, to identify each group within the puzzle. When complete, the entire puzzle will be made up of identified groups.",
