          "value": "These puzzles provide particularly good practice with number bonds. By using tokens instead of a pencil, you can use puzzle sheets over and over.\n\nCreate these puzzles by starting with an empty grid and putting in numbers around the grid using pairs and triples that add up to the target sum. It’s more fun if the puzzle has just one solution, but don’t worry about it.",
